                            <th>Th·ªùi gian k·∫øt th√∫c</th>
                            <th>Gi√° c∆° b·∫£n</th>
                            <th>H∆∞·ªõng</th>
                            <th>Tr·∫°ng th√°i</th>
                            <th>Thao t√°c</th>
                        </tr>
